title: VideoHive - Super Simple Slideshow - 11462220
description:
Quickly display your photos or videos in the Super Simple Slide Show After Effects Template! Available in 4K and HD1080

All animated scenes have a transition at the beginning but none at the end so you can overlap the scenes anyway you want in order to change the timing of the video. Future proof your project by creating a 4K version- no worries, it renders super fast!

In this video template youâ€™ll get 60 Placeholders including 8 animated text scenes. An HD1080 version is also included. The file has a modular structure so you can re-edit and re-arrange all the entire project.

Global color controls change the transition color and opacity for the entire project. Each animated text scene has a control panel for changing text colors, background color, and background box height, width and opacity.


Features:

    60 Placeholders for Photos or Videos
    8 Animated Text Scenes
    Video Tutorial Included
    Closing Scene with Logo and Text
    No Third Party Plugins
    Fast Render
    4K and HD1080 versions included
    Adobe After Effects CS4 and all newer versions
